{
  "stem": "2966.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You just run in order they shouldn't hit you, they shouldn't beat you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because beating was very terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was always very scared of beating.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were there a short time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were taken to a commando-- a camp that belonged to Buchenwald, a camp by the name of Ohrdruf.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This, as a matter of fact, is the first camp that General Eisenhower marched in with his American army.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the first camp he saw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was in that camp for a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was working.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They used to take us at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was very lucky to work at night always, somehow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were digging tunnels in a mountain where they were still planning to put factories in, even though they the war-- the war was almost at the end.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was already 1944.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Yeah, end of 1944.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were still planning to build factories on-- on the-- And the work was very hard, very brutal.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was very cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was winter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I saw that I will not survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was one barrack there in the camp where they kept people too sick to work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But they almost got as much food as the people that worked.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I thought to myself, I'd rather survive there if I'm going to survive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Without working, I have a better chance and a little food than working because I'll drop dead.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I somehow volunteered to go to that camp, which was dangerous, too, because they could take you out to the crematorium at any time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "People that didn't work had no value at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Even people that worked didn't have much of a value, but especially people that didn't work.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
